      Glenn's Emotional Plea To His Audience (Hear it at the 1:14:09 mark)

                   Thursday, July 24, 2014 11:14 AM






Glenn covers the controversy involving President Obama,
                           a motorcade and a woman in labor. 

He also discusses the press' coverage of Common Core 
             and shares his personal transformation with listeners.

 Joe Carr joins to discuss his run against Senator Lamar Alexander
            and Rabbi Irwin Kula talks about Michael Bloomberg's 
                strange reaction on CNN. 


                That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
